```

```css
[u2-intersect] {
    --u2-intersect-margin:-10%;
    --u2-intersect-threshold:1;
    background:#fbb;
}
[u2-intersect].u2-intersected { background:#bfb; }
[u2-intersect]::after {
    display:block;
    content:'below';
}
[u2-intersect].u2-intersected::after { content:'intersected'; }
[u2-intersect~="above"]::after { content:'above' }
```

